text: aur hamane banee isarail ko dariya ke us paar kar diya phir phiraun aur usake lashkar ne sarakashee kee aur sharaarat se unaka peechha kiya-yahaan tak ki jab vah doobane laga to kahane laga ki jis khuda par banee isarail eemaan lae hain mai bhee us par eemaan laata hoon usase siva koee maabood nahin aur main pharamaabaradaar bandon se hoon
